data.description: Charming classic cottage style home located in the heart of Minneapolis' Webber - Camden neighborhood! Beautiful remodeled property with 3 beds on 1 level. 2 full updated bathrooms. Brand new kitchen with ss appliances and granite counter tops. All new flooring throughout the house. Fenced yard with oversized 2 car garage. Great neighborhood, close to walking trails and shopping. Its a perfect first time buyer home!
